org.greencheek.processio.service.persistence.jmx
Class ProcessIOUsagePersistenceViaJmx

java.lang.Object
  org.greencheek.processio.service.persistence.jmx.ProcessIOUsagePersistenceViaJmx
All Implemented Interfaces:
ProcessIOUsagePersistence
public class ProcessIOUsagePersistenceViaJmx
extends Object
implements ProcessIOUsagePersistence

Persists a ProcessIOUsageHolder object in the JMXServer. This holder object holds onto a ProcessIO object that stores the current and previous io read and written by the process. The ProcessIOUsageHolder object is a JMX MXBean
